            "notes": "The main goal of this deck is to control the game through a combination of countermagic, removal spells, and card advantage. Tasigur, the Golden Fang serves as a powerful control commander, allowing the player to constantly manipulate their graveyard and reuse powerful spells. By including a mix of versatile removal spells like Abrupt Decay and Fatal Push, along with strong counterspells such as Cryptic Command and Force of Negation, the deck aims to disrupt the opponent's game plan while maintaining card advantage through draw spells like Brainstorm and Ponder. The deck also utilizes efficient creatures like Tarmogoyf and Snapcaster Mage to apply pressure and win the game once the opponent's resources have been exhausted."
